	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with your point dealing with whom needs LoH more. Yet, one needs to remember that the caster may have less HP than the warrior, he/she also way less armor too. So, even though the caster may not appear to be in dire straits that can change drastically, and being that caster is the one doing the enthralling, healing, or evacing, I recommend making sure he/she is alive and healthy. Especially, sorry warriors, since they can save the majority of the group and eliminate many corpse retrievals with one spell (i.e. enthralling a Mob before it can cause thing to get out of hand, healing the tank, evacing the group). One last thing, when soloing, try not to use LoH during the fight, you may find you need it after the fight (especially on the PvP servers). <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
